item.title: New Year Party Mix 2020 - DIMENSIONLESS #003
item.description: Yo, what's up fam? It's DJ Koustav here and I wish you all a very Happy and Prosperous New Year with lots of hopes and new beginnings for you. Also, I wanna present you my NEW YEAR MIX 2020 (3rd episode of the DIMENSIONLESS DJ Podcast) as a powerful dose of Electronic Dance Music to kickstart your year with lots of positivity and energy. Tracklist: provided on DJ Koustav Official facebook page.

item.title: EDM-BOLLYWOOD Non-Stop Dance Mix - DIMENSIONLESS #001
item.description: Introducing DIMENSIONLESS, the DJ Podcast featuring the dopest of EDM and the finest of Bollywood Dance Music. I am DJ Koustav (DJ & Producer, and a student) and this is my first podcast session. Though I wanted to include many more tracks from the epic producers, but, I could not manage time for a longer podcast session. Actually, DJing and Producing is my passion, and due to my studies, I cannot lend much time to these. However, I do always persue my passion and come up with something new everytime. So, stay tuned with me for my upcoming shows and releases. Enter the new Electronic Music Era and discover your World of possibilities in the Kingdom of DJ Koustav. Tracklist: #1 DJ Koustav - DIMENSIONLESS Intro #2 Bassjackers & MAKJ - Derp (Klo & Brille Remix) #3 Sexy Baliye - DJ Shadow Dubai Remix #4 Sweet Harmony vs No Money - Play Life Mashup (DJ NYK) #5 Badri Ki Dulhania (DJ Tejas Remix) #6 W&W x Vini Vici - Chakra (Original Mix) #7 Bolo Har Har Har (Shivaay) (Psy Trance Mashup) - DJ NYK #8 Ed Sheeran - Shape of You (Special Edit) #9 Laila Mein Laila (DJ Sunny Remix) #10 Cheez Badi (Remix) #11 DJ Snake - Let Me Love You (ft. Justin Bieber)(Original Mix) #12 Dimitri Vegas & Like Mike vs. VINAI - Louder (Original Mix) #13 David Guetta Dangerous (Banging Remix) #14 DJ Koustav - Infinity Hunt (Original Mix) #15 Kala Chashma (Baar Baar Dekho) (Remix) - DJ NYK #16 DJ Chetas - Tamma Tamma vs Bomb A Drop #17 Galti Se Mistake (Tapori Mix) - DJ Tejas #18 Trippy Trippy (Remix) - DJ Shadow Dubai #19 David Guetta - S.T.O.P (feat. Ryan Tedder)
